UserAdapter
public abstract class AbstractUserDetails
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.acegisecurity.userdetails.UserDetails

A base class to implement UserDetails from a supplied user domain object.

Helianto domain model allows for a two step authorization. Sub-classes must implement the getAuthorities() methods accordingly.

Author:
Mauricio Fernandes de Castro
